me":"2019-06-19T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"如果你或者身邊既人仲諗緊620、621好唔好出黎...請入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ecbc29aa0fc27f12ca86425e76ee0357f592c441","tid":1241474,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"你可以唔散架"},{"pid":"84ece6becc2b02176cb6d9cff9829aa23cbd456a","tid":1241474,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d27348938136c01b203947d72072a93f689a0884","tid":1241474,"uid":68483,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"其實有唔少人心水清都知叫散水係法律責任問題<br />\n只係過往歷史因素令人對散水反感啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"熱狗個d，口屌散水，次次有事走得最快係佢地。"}]}